hadiths[46]{hadithnumber,text}:
2390,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney sadqey sey ruju na karo. yani kisi ko sadqa dey kar wapis na lo."
2391,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs sadqa dey kar apna sadqa wapis ley leta hai, uski misal kuttey ki si hai jo qai karta hai, phir palat kar apni qai kha leta hai."
2392,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamanae Mubarak main eik ghoda sadqa kiya. phir (baad mein) unhoney dekha ke uska Malik (jisey wo ghoda sadqe key tor par diya gaya tha) usey kam qeemat par bech raha hai. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar uskey mutalliq masla daryaft kiya to aap ney farmaya : apna sadqa mat kharido."
2393,"Hazrat Zuber bin Awam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unka eik ghoda jis ka naam ghamar ya ghamraa tha, unhoney wo (bator sadqa kisi ko) sawari key liye dey diya. baad mein unhoney uskey eik bachhedey ya bachheiri ko biktaa dekha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen us (ko kharidney) sey mana kar diya."
2394,Hazrat Abdullah bin Barida (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb Aslami (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney farmaya : eik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey apni walida ko eik londi sadqe key taur par di thi. ab walida faut ho gaee hain. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ney tujhey ajr dey diya aur wo (londi) virasat key taur par terey paas wapis aa gaee.
2395,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur kaha : mainey apni walida ko apna eik baagh dey diya tha. (ab) wo faut ho gaee hain, aur merey ilawa koi waris chhod kar nahin gaeen. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tera sadqa durust ho gaya, aur tera baagh teri milkiyat mein wapis aa gaya."
2396,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko khaibar mein zamin mili to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur mashwara talab kartey huye arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey khaibar mein aisa maal mila hai ke meri nazar mein us sey umda maal mujhey kabhi nahin mila to aap mujhey kya hukm farmatey hain? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar tum chaho to asal zamin apney paas rakho aur us (ki pedawar) ko sadqa kar do. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney aisey hi kya, aur ye (shart laga di) ke asal zamin na bechi jaeygi, na ( kisi ko) hiba ki jaeygi aur na (kisi ko) virasat key tor par di jaeygi. aap ney wo zamin gharibon key liye, rishte-daaron key liye, Allah ki raah mein, musafiron aur mehmano key liye sadqa kar di, jo uska intizam karey is par gunah nahin ke is mein sey munasib had tak khaye ya dost ko khilaaey lekin us sey maal na kamaey."
2397,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! khaibar mein mujhey jo sau hissey miley hain, mujhey us sey pyara (aur behtar) maal kabhi nahin mila. mera irada hai ke unhen sadqa kar dun. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : asal (zameen) ko roke rakho aur uska phal Allah ki raah mein (sadqa) qarar dey do. (Imam Ibne-Maja key ustad) ibne-Abi umr ney kaha ke yehi hadees meri kitab main eik dusri jagah ''Sufiyan, an Abdullah, an Nafey an ibne-Umar'' ki sanad sey Hazrat umr sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
2398,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna hai : aariyatan (udhaar) li hui chiz wapis ki jaey aur doodh key liye liya huwa janwer wapis kiya jaey."
2399,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : aariyatan (udhaar) li hui chiz wapis ki jaey aur doodh key liye liya huwa janwer wapis kiya jaey."
2400,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haath ney jo kuchh (qarz ya Aariyat (udhaar) key taur par) liya , wo uskey zimmey rehta hai yahan tak key usey ada karey."
2401,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis key paas amanat rakhi gaee ho (aur wo ittifaaq se zaya ho jaey) to is par tawaan (jurmaana) nahin hoga."
2402,"Hazrat Urwa bin Abu-Ja'ad Baarqi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen bakri kharidney key liye eik Dinar diya. usney do bakriyan kharid lein, phir eik bakri eik Dinar ki bech di aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein Dinar bhi pesh kar diya aur bakri bhi. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uskey haq mein barkat ki dua farmaai. Raavi kehtey hain (iskey baad un ki ye haalat thi ke) agar wo mitti bhi khareedtey to is mein bhi unhen nafa mil jata. Hazrat Urwa bin Abu-Ja'ad Baarqi (Raziallahu anhu) sey dusri riwayat mein ye alfaz hain, unhoney farmaya : bahar sey maale tijarat aaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey eik Dinar diya----.  iskey baad pura waaqiyaa bayan farmaya."
2403,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : dolat waley ka taal matol karna zulm hai. aur tum mein sey kisi ko jab maal daar aadmi ka hawala diya jaey to usey chahiye ke hawala qubul kar ley."
2404,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : dolat waley ka taal matol karna zulm hai aur agar tujhey kisi maal daar aadmi ka hawala diya jaey to qubul kar."
2405,"Hazrat Abu-Umama Baahli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : zamanat deney waley par tawaan (jurmaana) hoga aur qarz ada kiya jaeyga."
2406,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney main eik aadmi key zimmey dusron key das Dinar they. wo har waqt maqrooz key sath rehney laga. maqrooz ney kaha : tujhey deney ko merey paas kuch nahin. usney kaha : Allah ki qism ! main tujhey nahin chhodunga yahan tak key to mera qarz ada karey ya koi zaamin pesh karey. wo usey khinch kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley aaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to isey kitney arsey ki mohlat deta hai? usney kaha : eik mahiney ki. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main iski zimmey daari uthata (zamanat deta) hun. maqrooz Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key farmaai huye waqt par hazir ho gaya . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey farmaya : tujhey ye maal kahan sey mila? usney kaha : eik kaan sey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is mein koi bhalai nahin. aur khud uska qarz ada kar diya.
2407,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Haris bin Rabee Ansari) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, (unhoney farmaya : ) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik janaza laya gaya taake aap uski namaze janaza ada farmaain to aap ney farmaya : tum log apney sathi ka janaza padh lo (main nahin padhunga) is par qarz hai. Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kya : main iski zimmey-daari uthata hun. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (zimme-daari) puri karogey? unhoney kaha : puri karunga. aur uska qarz atthaara ya unnis dirham tha."
2408,Hazrat Imran bin Huzefa (Rahimahullah) Ummul-mominin Hazrat Memuna binte Haris (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat kartey hain ke wo qarz liya karti thin. unkey ghar key kisi fard ney us ko na-munasib samajhtey huye arz kiya : aap aisa na kiya karen. unhoney farmaya : kyon na lun? mainey apney Nabi aur apney mehbub (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye farman suna hai : jo musalman qarz leta hai aur Allah ko uskey barey mein ye ilm hota hai ke wo isey ada karney ka irada rakhta hai to Allah Taala uska qarz duniya hi mein utaar deta hai.
2409,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala qarz leney waley key sath hota hai yahan tak key wo qarz ada kar dey, jabkey (qarz) us kaam key liye na ho jo Allah ko na-pasand hai. Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu anhuma) apney khazanchi sey kaha kartey they : jao ! merey liye qarz ley aao. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka ye farman sunney key baad main pasand nahin karta ke main koi raat (is tarah) guzaarun ke Allah merey sath na ho."
2410,"Hazrat Suhebul Khair (Suheb Romi) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs qarz leta hai aur uska pukhta irada hota hai ke usey wapis nahin kerega, wo Allah ko chor bin kar milega. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney eik dusri sanad sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey isi mazmoon ki hadees bayan ki hai."
2411,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs logon ka maal usey zaya karney key iradey sey leta hai, Allah usey tabah kar dega."
2412,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ki jaan us haal mein uskey jism sey nikli ke wo teen chizon sey pak tha, wo jannat mein dakhil ho jaeyga : takabbur sey, maale-ghanimat ki khayanat sey aur qarz sey."
2413,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin ki rooh uskey qarz ki wajeh sey latakti rehti hai yahan tak key uski taraf sey (qarz) ada kar diya jaey."
2414,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs is haal mein faut huwa ke uskey zimmey eik Dinar ya eik dirham tha, wo uski nekiyon sey ada kya jaeyga, wahan (aakhirat mein) Dinar hongey na dirham."
2415,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamanae Mubarak mein jab koi momin maqrooz ho kar faut hota to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey barey mein poochhtey aur farmatey : kya usney apney qarz ki adaegi ka saman chhoda hai? agar log kehtey : haan to aap uska janaza padhatey aur agar log kehtey : nahin to aap farmatey : apney sathi ka janaza padh lo. jab Allah Taala ney apney Nabi ko futoohaat (aur ghaneematein) ata farmaeen to aap ney farmaya : main mominon sey un ki janon sey bhi ziyada talluq rakhta hun, isliye jo koi maqrooz faut hoga to uskey qarz ki adaegi merey zimmey hai aur jo koi maal chhod kar faut ho jaeyga to wo maal uskey warison ka hai."
2416,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo koi maal chhod jaey to wo uskey warison ka hai aur jo koi qarz ya chhotey bachchey chhod jaey to uski adaegi aur un ki nigehdasht (dekh-bhaal) merey zimmey hai. aur main mominon sey sab sey ziyada talluq rakhney wala hun (ya unka ziyada zimmey daar hun)."
2417,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney kisi tang dast par aasani ki to Allah Taala duniya aur aakhirat mein usey aasani ata farmaeyga."
2418,"Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi tang dast ko mohlat deta hai, usey har roz sadqey ka sawab milta hai. aur jisney wajibul-adaa honey key baad mazeed mohlat di, usey bhi yehi sawab milta hai, (yani) har roz sadqey ka sawab hota hai."
2419,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Sahabi Hazrat Abu Yousr (Kaab bin Amr Sulami (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs pasand karta hai ke Allah Taala usey apney saye mein jagah dey to usey chahiye ke tang dast ko mohlat dey ya uska qarz maaf kar dey."
2420,"Hazrat Huzefa (bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhuma)) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik aadmi faut ho gaya. usey kaha gaya : tu ney kon sa (nek) amal kiya hai? usey yad aa gaya, ya yad dilaaya gaya to usney kaha : main sikkey aur naqdi mein chashm poshi (nazar andaaz) karta tha aur tang dast ko (qarz ki adaegi mein) mohlat dey diya karta tha. Allah Taala ney usey maaf kar diya. Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey bhi Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye hadees suni hai."
2421,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) aur Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo koi apna haq talab karey, usey chahiye ke sharafat sey talab karey, pura ada ho ya adhuraa."
2422,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney haq waley (qarz chahney wale) sey farmaya : apna haq sharafat sey wasul karo, pura ada ho ya adhuraa."
2423,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey ziyada behtar log wo hain jo achchhey tareeqey sey ada kartey hain."
2424,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abu-Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey ghazwae Hunain key moqey par tees hazar ya chaalis hazar qarz liya. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ghazwe sey wapis) tashrif laye to unhen qarz ada kar diya, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah terey ghar baar mein aur terey maal mein barkat ata farmaaey. udhaar ka badla (qarz ki) adaegi aur shukriya ada karna hai."
2425,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey qarz wapis maangney aaya , ya kisi aur maali haq ka mutalba karney aaya. usney kuchh (na munasib) alfaz kahey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney usko saza dene ka irada kiya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ruk jao, qarz waley ko apney sathi (maqrooz) par ikhtiyar hota hai, jab tak wo adaegi na kar dey."
2426,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik baddoo (ea'raab) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey apney kisi qarz ka taqaza karney aaya jo aap key zimmey tha. usney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sakht lehje mein baat ki, yahan tak key yahan tak keh diya : agar aap ada nahin kerengey to main aap key sath sakht ravaiya ikhtiyar karunga. Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney usey daantaa aur kaha : tujh par afsos ! kya tujhey malum nahin to kis sey mukhatib hai? usney kaha : main to apna haq mang raha hun. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum ney haq waley ka sath kyon na diya? phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat khaula binte Qais (Raziallahu anha) ko pegham bheja : agar tumharey paas khajuren hain to hamein qarz dey do, hamari khajuren aayengi to hum tumhara qarz ada kar dengey. unhoney kaha : merey maa baap aap par qurban, aey Allah key Rasool ! main hukm ki taameel karungi. unhoney aap ko (khajuren) qarz dey den. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ka qarz ada kiya aur usey khana khilaya. usney kaha : aap ney mujhey pura haq dey diya, Allah aap ko pura dey to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aisey log behtareen hotey hain. wo qom paak nahin hoti jis mein kamzor ko pareshan kiye baghair uska haq na diya jaaey."
2427,"Hazrat Amr bin Shareed (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Shareed Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : adaegi ki taqat rakhney wala taal matol karey to uski be-Izzati karna aur usey saza dena jayez ho jata hai. (Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key ustaad) Ali bin Muhammad Tanaafusi (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : be Izzatii karney sey murad uski shikayat karna aur saza sey murad qaid karna hai."
2428,"Hazrat Harmaas bin Habib (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Hazrat Habib bin Solba) sey aur wo Harmaas key dada (Hazrat Solba Tameemi Anbari (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : main apney eik maqrooz ko ley kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. aap ney mujh sey farmaya : (ye jahan jaey) iskey sath raho. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Sham key waqt merey paas sey guzrey to farmaya : aey bani Tameem key bhai ! tumharey qaidi ka kya bana?"
2429,"Hazrat Kaab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney masjid mein Hazrat Abdullah bin Abu Hadrad (Raziallahu anhu) sey unkey zimmey apney qarz ki wapsi ka taqaza kiya. un ki aawazen buland ho gaeen yahan tak key Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apney ghar mein un ki aawazen sun lein. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahar nikal kar unkey paas tashrif laye aur Hazrat Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) ko aawaz di, unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! main hazir hun. aap ney farmaya : apney qarz mein sey itna maaf kar do. aur haath sey nisf (aadhe) ka ishara kiya (aadha qarz chhod do). unhoney kaha : mainey maaf kiya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (ibne Abu Hadrad (Raziallahu anhu) sey) farmaya : utho, iska qarz ada karo."
2430,"Hazrat Qais bin Romi (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Aznaan (Rahimahullah) ney Hazrat Alqama (Rahimahullah) ko unka wazeefa (tankhwaah) milney tak ki muddat key liye eik hazar dirham qarz diya. jab unhen wazeefa mila to unhon (Suleman) ney un sey sakhti sey (qarz ki wapsi ka) taqaza kiya. Alqama (Rahimahullah) ney adaegi kar di lekin unhen narazi mehsus hui (ke itni sakhti sey taqaza kiya hai) chand maah thehar kar wo (phir) unkey paas aaye aur kaha : mujhey tankhwaah milney tak eik hazar dirham qarz dey den. unhoney kaha : haan, (main badi khushi sey aap ka) ehtiraam kartey huye (aap ko qarz deta hun, phir apni biwi sey kaha) : aey Umme Utba ! tumharey paas jo mehar band thaili hai, wo ley aao. wo ley aayen to (Alqama sey) kaha : qism hai Allah ki ! ye aap key wohi dirham hain jo aap ney mujhey ada kiye they. mainey in mein sey eik dirham bhi idhar-udhar nahin kiya. Alqama (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : kya khub ! aap ney mujh sey jo sulook kiya, iski kya wajeh? unhoney kaha : (iski wajeh wo hadees thi) jo mainey aap sey suni. unhoney kaha : aap ney mujh sey kon si hadees suni? Suleman (Alaihissalam) ney kaha : mainey aap (Alqama) ko Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey suna ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo musalman doosrey musalman ko dobara qarz deta hai, wo eik baar itna sadqa karney key barabar ho jata hai. Alqama (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : mujhey Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney (waqaee) isi tarah hadees sunai thi."
2431,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Meraj ki raat mainey jannat key darwazey par likha huwa dekha : sadqey ka sawab das guna hai aur qarz ka atthaara guna. mainey kaha : aey Jibril ! kya wajeh hai ke qarz sadqey sey bhi ziyada fazilat ka hamil hai? unhoney kaha : isliye ke saail ( baaz oqaat) sawal karta hai, halanke uskey paas ( uski zarurat ka maal) mojud hota hai jabkey qarz leney wala zarurat (aur majburi (ki haalat hi mein qarz leta hai) kyonkey qarz ki wapsi to zaruri hai, isliye majburi key waqt hi liya jata hai) ."
2432,"Hazrat Yahya bin Abu-Ishaq Hunaai (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : eik aadmi apney bhai ko maal bataur qarz deta hai, phir wo (maqrooz) usey kuch tohfa dey deta hai (kya ye munasib hai?) unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs jab (kisi ko) qarz dey, phir (maqrooz) usey tohfa dey ya sawari key liye janwer pesh karey to (qarz khaah ko chahiye ke wo is par sawari na karey aur na wo (tohfa) qubul kerey. siwaye uskey ke un dono mein pehley sey (tohfey ka) ye silsila jari ho."
2433,"Hazrat Saad bin Atwal johni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unka bhai faut ho gaya, usney teen so dirham (tarka) chhoda aur baal bachey bhi chhodey . mainey chaha ke ye maal uskey biwi bachon par kharch karun . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara bhai apney qarz ki wajeh sey qaid hai, isliye uska qarz ada karo . to Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey uska ( sara) qarz ada kar diya hai, siwaye do Dinar key . eik aurat unka daawa karti hai lekin uskey paas koi sabut ( gawahi waghera) nahin . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey dey do , wo sachi hai."
2434,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke unkey walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin haram Ansari (Raziallahu anhu)) faut huye to unkey zimmey eik Yahudi ka tees wasq ghalla qarz tha. Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) ney us sey mohlat maangi to usney mohlat deney sey inkar kar diya, to Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey guzarish ki ke Yahudi sey un ki sifarish kar den , chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney tashrif ley ja kar Yahudi sey baat cheet ki (aur ye pesh kaash! ki) ke un par jo qarz hai uskey badley wo un ki khajuron ka sara phal ley ley to us ( yahudi) ney ye baat manney sey inkar kar diya . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ko mohlat deney ka kaha to usney us sey bhi inkar kar diya . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khajuron key baagh mein tashrif ley gaey aur darakhton key darmiyan chaley , phir Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : phal utaaro aur usey uska haq pura dey do . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key tashrif ley janey key baad unhoney phal utaar kar teen wasq khajuren us (yahudi) ko dey den aur baara wasq khajuren bach gaeen. Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) us waqiey ki khabar deney key liye Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye to dekha ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mojud nahin . jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney khidmat mein hazir ho kar ittilaa di ke unhoney us (yahudi) ko puri adaegi kar di hai, aur jo miqdaar bach gaee thi wo bhi batai, chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : umr bin Khattab ko bhi ye baat batao . Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) key paas ja kar unhen ye baat batai to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us ( baagh) mein chal rahey they to mujhey usi waqt yaqin ho gaya tha ke Allah Taala us phal mein zarur barkat ata farmaeyga."
2435,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din maqrooz sey qarz wasul kya jaeyga, jab wo (maqrooz ho kar) faut ho jaeyga magar jo shakhs teen kamon key liye qarz leta hai) wo us sey mustashna hai. (wo shakhs jiski Allah key raastey mein) jihad karney ki) quwat kam ho jati hai to wo Allah key dushman aur apney dushman ka muqabla karney ki taqat hasil karney key liye qarz leta hai. ( doosra) wo shakhs jis key paas koi musalman faut hota hai aur uskey paas qarz liye baghair uskey kafan dafn ki gunjaaish nahin hoti . aur (teesra) wo shakhs jisey apney be nikah rehney ki surat mein (gunah mein mulawwis honey ka khatra mehsus kar key) Allah sey khof aata hai, wo apney Deen (mein kharabi) key dar sey (qarz ley kar) nikah kar leta hai. Allah Taala qiyamat key din un (teen qism key afrad) ka qarz ada kar dega ."
